{"tid":2114974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買琴問題","createTime":"2020-07-19T08:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T09:16:09.000Z","uid":319870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f547f19278ff31979072f8c790ee54a5a0b2d14","tid":2114974,"uid":319870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"睇中2款鋼琴，YAMAHA JU109同埋U1<br />\nJU109係因為啱晒屋企SIZE，唔係有一邊突起，全新就217200，2 手鋼琴公司就15000，5年內，有證書，都係包10年保養，搬運，2次調音。<br />\nU1 2手鋼琴公司就15000，20年琴齡，有證書都係包10年保養，搬運，2次調音，如何放屋企就會突起，但屋企人傾過之後，佢地都接受。我上carousell睇過，15-20年琴齡，有證書都係18000-23000，但就咩都唔包(保養，搬運，調音)，會有基本野(櫈，布，暖管)。<br />\n我就傾向U1 2手鋼琴公司，因為都好大決心學，想一部琴考到8級，同埋自己真係有興趣學，各位巴絲打有冇咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8293033a06e232725e2f99a6da253df714de0f58","tid":2114974,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"個人認為你係有心學嘅<br />\n咩琴都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正你去考試嗰陣部琴係三角琴<br />\n同平時嘅琴手感唔太同"},{"pid":"8db6419f8e83933fc1948afb2b72edab8f702a41","tid":2114974,"uid":155725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"萬零蚊喎...20年琴U1都未去到咁低既價錢啦<br />\n<br />\n私人轉讓睇落好似貴啲又唔包保養調音，<br />\n但你要諗通常正常黎計家用琴都唔會有改裝問題，但琴倉好多古怪野..."},{"pid":"96140d7d69e217b9ef6cef8eeb7d5dcd3a452bcc","tid":2114974,"uid":319870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8293033a06e232725e2f99a6da253df714de0f58","tid":2114974,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"個人認為你係有心學嘅<br />\n咩琴都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正你去考試嗰陣部琴係三角琴<br />\n同平時嘅琴手感唔太同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T